Class TabButtonGroup

java.lang.Object
  de.must.appletserver.TabButtonGroup
All Implemented Interfaces:
AppletTalker, Remotable
public class TabButtonGroup
extends java.lang.Object
implements Remotable

A group of buttons to be laid-out in one line, e.g. to switch between different panel analogously to Swing's tabbed pane. Used in pure Servlet context. JSP equivalent @see TabButtonGroupForJsp
